name: Strawberry
description: Strawberries are soft, sweet, bright red berries. Strawberries have tiny edible seeds. When ripe, strawberries smell wonderful.

name: Chicken
description: Chicken meat is known by its nutritional quality, as it contains significant amount of high-quality and easily digestible protein.

name: Butterfish
description: The butterfish is a small, round fish distinguishable by its thin, deep body and lack of pelvic or ventral fins. It has soft-rayed dorsal.

name: Orange
description: The orange is a usually round or oval citrus; its rind and flesh are generally orange. It's edible part is consumed in fresh or in juice.

name: Lamb Leg
description: Only the two hind legs produce the cut referred to as 'leg of lamb'. It is a large, lean, and tender cut and can be used whole or subdivided.

name: Nuts
description: Nuts are actually dry fruits. Single-seeded fruits that have high oil content. They are usually enclosed in a leathery or solid outer layer.

name: Beef Steak
description: A beefsteak, often called just steak, is a flat cut of beef with parallel faces, usually cut perpendicular to the muscle fibers.

name: Broccoli
description: Broccoli is a fast-growing annual plant. Upright and branching with leathery leaves, broccoli bears dense green clusters of flower buds.

name: Cookies
description: A cookie is a baked or cooked snack or dessert that is typically small, flat and sweet. It contains flour, sugar, egg, oil, butter.

name: Dates
description: Dates are small, sweet fruits that grow in date palm trees. Dried dates have a very high amount of sugar of their total weight.

name: Sea Bass
description: Sea bass are rather perchlike fish. Generally elongated body has small scales, the mouth is large, and the tail is straight-edged or rounded.

name: Shripms
description: Shrimp are characterized by a semitransparent body flattened from side to side and a flexible abdomen terminating in a fanlike tail.
